snippet: Scott Wiener, a first-term supervisor and lifelong Democrat who sponsored antinudity legislation, has played a big role in pulling fellow supervisors toward the middle.
abstract: Scott Wiener, a first-term member of San Francisco Board of Supervisors and lifelong Democrat who sponsored antinudity legislation, has played a big role in pulling fellow supervisors toward the middle by focusing on quality-of-life issues.
lead_paragraph: Scott Wiener, a first-term supervisor and lifelong Democrat who sponsored antinudity legislation, has played a big role in pulling fellow supervisors toward the middle.
